rformance_Metrics_URL - Budget_Allocated - Cost_Actual - ROI_Percentage SHEET 5: Generation Logs Columns: - Log_ID - Timestamp - Platform_Used (Freepik/Higgsfield/Pletor/Sora2/Veo3) - Prompt_Used - Parameters_JSON - Generation_Time_Seconds - Cost_USD - Output_URL - Quality_Rating - Error_Message (if failed) - Retry_Count Create a visual representation showing how these sheets interconnect and support the automation workflow. Use professional color coding and clear relationships between sheets. Include sample"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=9f871a60-d05f-4314-a40e-4ebf58758f50","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=9f871a60-d05f-4314-a40e-4ebf58758f50"}]}]}]
